  '<li><strong>Day-in-month sanity</strong> — Feb 30 / Apr 31 etc. refused (light Gregorian table; non-leap-year February is structural-shape).</li>',
  '<li><strong>BIDI / zero-width / control / null-byte</strong> — universal-refuse same codepoint catalog as the rest of the family.</li>',
  '</ul>',

